{
  "page": "Mermaids (Merling Queen's)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Merling_Queen_by_tonyloom.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/86/The_Merling_Queen_by_tonyloom.jpg/300px-The_Merling_Queen_by_tonyloom.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/86/The_Merling_Queen_by_tonyloom.jpg/450px-The_Merling_Queen_by_tonyloom.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/86/The_Merling_Queen_by_tonyloom.jpg/600px-The_Merling_Queen_by_tonyloom.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Merling_Queen_by_tonyloom.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The <a href=\"/index.php/Merling_Queen\" title=\"Merling Queen\">Merling Queen</a> and her Mermaids, by tonyloom.</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>Mermaids</b> are four attendants of the <a href=\"/index.php/Merling_Queen\" title=\"Merling Queen\">Merling Queen</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Courtesan\" title=\"Courtesan\">courtesan</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Duties\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Duties</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Duties\">Duties</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mermaids_(Merling_Queen%27s)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Duties\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Young <a href=\"/index.php/Maiden\" title=\"Maiden\">maidens</a> who have just <a href=\"/index.php/Flowering\" title=\"Flowering\">flowered</a>, the Mermaids accompany the <a href=\"/index.php/Merling_Queen\" title=\"Merling Queen\">Merling Queen</a> everywhere and tend to her train and hair.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mermaids_(Merling_Queen%27s)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>One of the Mermaids drowned at some point.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mermaids_(Merling_Queen%27s)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mermaids_(Merling_Queen%27s)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a> informs the <a href=\"/index.php/Kindly_man\" title=\"Kindly man\">kindly man</a> that the <a href=\"/index.php/Merling_Queen\" title=\"Merling Queen\">Merling Queen</a> has chosen a new Mermaid to take the place of the one that drowned. The new one is the daughter of a <a href=\"/index.php/Prestayn_family\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Prestayn family\">Prestayn</a> serving maid, thirteen and penniless. The kindly man considers that they are all lovely, at the beginning.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mermaids_(Merling_Queen%27s)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Every <a href=\"/index.php/Courtesan\" title=\"Courtesan\">courtesan</a> had her own barge, and servants to pole her to her trysts. The <a href=\"/index.php/Poetess\" title=\"Poetess\">Poetess</a> always had a book to hand, the <a href=\"/index.php/Moonshadow\" title=\"Moonshadow\">Moonshadow</a> wore only white and silver, and the <a href=\"/index.php/Merling_Queen\" title=\"Merling Queen\">Merling Queen</a> was never seen without her Mermaids, four young maidens in the blush of their first flowering who held her train and did her hair.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mermaids_(Merling_Queen%27s)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_34\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 34\">Chapter 34</a>, Cat Of The Canals.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_45\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 45\">Chapter 45</a>, The Blind Girl.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404134041\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.021 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.022 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 451/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8738/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 2086/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 496/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1558/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   11.563      1 -total\n 75.16%    8.691      4 Template:Ref\n 48.02%    5.552      4 Template:Ref/core\n 18.66%    2.158      1 Template:Quote\n 16.84%    1.947      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:15698-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404134041 and revision id 322564\n -->\n",
